This is the Quizly component.  It can be used to create
Quizly Exercises as GCB lessons. 

Source code:
Besides the __init.py__ file in this directory, the source
code for this component resides in assets/lib.

Update:
To update the source code, obtain the gcb-quizly.zip file
containing all of the Quizly source files from the main
Quizly directory (/Applications/MAMP/htdocs/quizly) and
unzip it in the asset/lib directory.  